9
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:24,320
Suqin.

10
00:01:25,240 --> 00:01:26,000
Prepare the dishes.

11
00:01:29,280 --> 00:01:31,000
I didn't know you were here.

12
00:01:31,240 --> 00:01:32,000
Sorry for not welcoming you.

13
00:01:32,440 --> 00:01:33,240
Cut the crap.

14
00:01:33,680 --> 00:01:34,840
Bring me good wine and dishes.

15
00:01:38,080 --> 00:01:41,039
A commoner has played tricks on me many times.

16
00:01:42,160 --> 00:01:43,800
I'll teach you a lesson today.

17
00:02:00,880 --> 00:02:01,920
You want to die?

18
00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:03,720
What are you doing?

19
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:06,440
This is Prince Xiao.

20
00:02:06,440 --> 00:02:07,600
How old are you?

21
00:02:08,120 --> 00:02:09,400
Your Highness.

22
00:02:10,440 --> 00:02:12,680
Do you think I don't know who you are?

23
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:15,200
You already gave up your right as the Crown Prince.

24
00:02:15,320 --> 00:02:16,680
That is me.

25
00:02:18,600 --> 00:02:19,720
Listen.

26
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:21,320
From now on,

27
00:02:21,600 --> 00:02:23,680
