28
00:02:24,120 --> 00:02:26,600
until you give up Xu Sanniang.

29
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:30,640
Otherwise, Fusu County will be destroyed because of you.

30
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:34,160
How dare you threaten me?

31
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:38,800
So what?

32
00:02:44,079 --> 00:02:46,520
My lord.

33
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:48,160
Wei Dabao and his men retreat for 20 miles.

34
00:02:48,160 --> 00:02:50,040
It's said that the inner chamberlain has an urgent order.

35
00:02:50,040 --> 00:02:51,200
He's afraid of being attacked by the Japanese.

36
00:02:51,200 --> 00:02:52,120
My lord...

37
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:55,400
Go find Wenjun.

38
00:02:55,400 --> 00:02:56,240
Yes, my lord.

39
00:03:01,920 --> 00:03:02,760
Raise your hands.

40
00:03:03,440 --> 00:03:04,240
Squat down.

41
00:03:04,480 --> 00:03:05,480
Straighten your arms.

42
00:03:05,880 --> 00:03:06,560
Keep your legs steady.

43
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:08,120
You can only move when the enemy moves.

44
00:03:08,440 --> 00:03:09,240
Got it?

45
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:10,600
Yes.

46
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:22,000
That's all for today's morning.

47
00:03:22,200 --> 00:03:23,200
We'll continue in the afternoon.

48
00:03:23,480 --> 00:03:24,280
Dismissed.

49
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:26,040
Okay.

50
00:03:26,040 --> 00:03:27,079
Let's go home.

51
00:03:29,040 --> 00:03:29,840
This way, please.

52
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:31,880
We have a few new dishes.

53
00:03:31,880 --> 00:03:32,600
Please have a taste.

54
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:33,360
Sir.

55
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:35,040
Please try the new dish.

56
00:03:35,880 --> 00:03:36,440
Who is that?

57
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:38,600
Go away.

58
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:41,920
Your Highness.

59
00:03:46,040 --> 00:03:47,079
What are you doing here?

60
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:50,000
The legitimate son pretended to be a poor scholar.

61
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:50,720
Your Highness.

62
00:03:51,040 --> 00:03:53,840
Did you have a good time in "Phoenix Begging the Phoenix"?

63
00:03:56,640 --> 00:03:58,920
