92
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:41,040
Why are you looking at me?

93
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:41,840
Not me.

94
00:05:44,680 --> 00:05:45,520
Miss Wei,

95
00:05:46,080 --> 00:05:48,120
There must be some misunderstanding between us.

96
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:49,520
Actually, I'm married.

97
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:51,680
This is my wife, General Seo Chun-sim.

98
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:53,440
Can you report this to the court?

99
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:56,280
Did General Xu enter the ancestral book?

100
00:05:56,880 --> 00:05:58,240
If there's no one,

101
