111
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:20,240
Besides, our engagement has been delayed for a long time.

112
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:21,520
It's good for both of us

113
00:06:21,520 --> 00:06:22,840
It's good for both of us.

114
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,400
You agreed to marry her?

115
00:06:32,640 --> 00:06:35,040
I know you have feelings for General Xu.

116
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:36,000
Not to mention men.

117
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:37,840
